WEBVTT

00:31.532 --> 00:32.950
- Look. Come on!
- Run!

01:02.646 --> 01:03.814
Thanks.

01:11.530 --> 01:13.448
I'm sorry. I didn't know who else to call.

01:16.326 --> 01:17.327
You okay?

01:19.663 --> 01:21.415
No. I don't know.

01:23.625 --> 01:26.378
I thought at least some things in my life
made sense.

01:28.714 --> 01:32.342
This makes sense. You and me.

01:41.018 --> 01:43.270
I found out something about my mum.

01:44.813 --> 01:46.732
I guess she was sick.

01:46.815 --> 01:48.233
Psychotic disorder.

01:49.693 --> 01:52.821
My therapist told me
it could be hereditary.

01:57.451 --> 01:59.703
You should've seen the way
she looked at me.

02:00.871 --> 02:02.998
So concerned.

02:03.999 --> 02:06.919
I'm just so sick of people
looking at me like that.

02:07.503 --> 02:10.923
It just feels like all anyone sees
is this baggage.

02:11.590 --> 02:13.592
What I did, what they think I did.

02:14.259 --> 02:15.594
Every time I'm ten minutes late,

02:15.677 --> 02:18.138
someone thinks I've gone
and jumped off a bridge.

02:18.222 --> 02:20.015
There's nothing wrong with you, Sophie.

02:20.849 --> 02:22.184
But what if there is?

02:22.893 --> 02:26.980
What if this is something
that's always been in me?

02:27.481 --> 02:28.899
You decide who you are.

02:32.945 --> 02:34.613
Yeah. I hope you're right.

02:35.822 --> 02:36.823
Look at me.

02:39.034 --> 02:40.744
I know this situation you're in,

02:42.162 --> 02:45.123
it feels like you're at the center
of it all, but you didn't do this.

02:45.207 --> 02:47.251
This was other people's crimes.

02:48.335 --> 02:49.711
You just got caught up in it.

02:57.970 --> 03:00.514
I don't wanna go back
to that perfect house,

03:01.682 --> 03:03.559
pretend to be the good wife.

03:05.227 --> 03:07.855
You know,
you won't have to pretend much longer.

03:09.314 --> 03:10.858
I got a meeting today.

03:10.941 --> 03:13.277
I get what I need,
they'll arrest James tonight.

03:16.780 --> 03:20.158
- Holy shit. We're doing this.
- Yeah. We're doing this.

04:50.290 --> 04:52.584
<i>You've reached Sophie Ellis.
Leave a message.</i>

04:57.673 --> 04:59.675
- Looks like they're done now.
- Thanks.

05:00.300 --> 05:02.803
I'm gonna be out for lunch,
so you text me if anything comes up.

05:02.886 --> 05:03.887
Of course.

05:04.972 --> 05:06.765
What up, buddy?
We gonna lunch like ladies or what?

05:06.849 --> 05:07.850
Sure.

05:08.433 --> 05:10.435
Perk up. You're buying today.

05:12.020 --> 05:13.272
What are you talking about?

05:14.815 --> 05:16.567
You said you needed help. I'm helping.

05:19.945 --> 05:22.322
Sorry. Nope. Short lunch today.

05:25.075 --> 05:26.618
I got a loan. Just came in.

05:26.702 --> 05:29.329
The escrow just cleared 20 minutes ago.
It's a done deal.

05:29.413 --> 05:32.457
There are some strings, but nothing
we can't cut loose down the road.

05:33.166 --> 05:34.835
Fuck me.

05:34.918 --> 05:36.086
Yeah, fuck you is right.

05:36.170 --> 05:38.380
What about the investigation?

05:38.463 --> 05:40.048
Funds will hit the account tonight.

05:40.132 --> 05:42.634
By tomorrow, the only thing
MacKenzie will be focused on

05:42.718 --> 05:45.429
is rebooking that girls' trip to Cabo.

05:45.512 --> 05:48.807
And the fact that this is wire fraud,
I mean, Miranda's just gonna ignore that?

05:48.891 --> 05:51.602
So the board finds out we moved
some money for the sake of optics.

05:51.685 --> 05:54.438
What do you think they're gonna do?
Set a Zoom with the FBI?

05:56.398 --> 05:58.400
What about your thing?
Did that come through?

05:58.483 --> 05:59.902
It will.

05:59.985 --> 06:01.069
Good. Great.

06:01.570 --> 06:02.821
Yeah.

06:02.905 --> 06:05.282
Hey, buddy. Relax.

06:05.365 --> 06:06.366
Yeah.

06:06.450 --> 06:10.120
Now you're just a regular rich guy,
in debt up to his balls.

06:10.204 --> 06:13.832
But a criminal?
Nah, you were never cool enough for that.

06:25.552 --> 06:26.678
Hey, Vic.

06:26.762 --> 06:28.555
- Hey.
- You taking lunch?

06:28.639 --> 06:33.519
Kyle should be here any minute to cover.
Tell him I'll be back in 45?

06:33.602 --> 06:35.020
Yeah, sure. No problem.

06:51.078 --> 06:52.120
Okay. Fuck.

07:00.754 --> 07:02.089
Okay.

07:11.765 --> 07:14.059
Hold on. I left something in the office.

07:14.142 --> 07:15.769
- I'll meet you over there.
- Okay.

07:22.818 --> 07:25.737
Hell yeah, baby. Easy money.

07:29.700 --> 07:30.868
Okay.

07:53.891 --> 07:55.726
Hey, you're back.

07:55.809 --> 07:57.144
What are you doing in here?

07:58.228 --> 08:00.689
I was just thirsty.

08:02.399 --> 08:05.068
Boss forgot his wallet
going to some fancy lunch.

08:05.152 --> 08:07.196
Guess he has something to celebrate.

08:12.242 --> 08:14.661
If you could restock the fridge,
that'd be great.

08:15.287 --> 08:16.914
Yeah, sure. No problem.

08:32.888 --> 08:35.474
Let's go. Come on.

08:35.557 --> 08:36.683
Let's go.

08:37.643 --> 08:38.644
Yes.

08:55.786 --> 08:56.828
You cold?

08:57.913 --> 08:58.914
I'm fine.

09:04.962 --> 09:06.255
I know that look.

09:08.507 --> 09:10.592
Same look you give me
every time you're about to leave.

09:11.927 --> 09:14.513
I told you, I don't have anywhere to be.

09:30.779 --> 09:31.864
I gotta take this.

09:35.826 --> 09:37.619
- Hey.
- Hey, man. It's me.

09:37.703 --> 09:39.746
I did it. I got everything you asked for.

09:39.830 --> 09:40.831
Where are you?

09:41.498 --> 09:43.125
I'm on lunch. But I can meet tonight.

09:43.208 --> 09:45.502
No, we need to do it now.
I'll pick you up.

09:47.087 --> 09:47.921
Fuck. Okay.

09:48.630 --> 09:50.507
<i>Hey, you got any more of those pills?</i>

09:50.591 --> 09:52.593
Are you really asking me
for drugs right now?

09:53.385 --> 09:57.014
Well, I mean, I did the job.
So, don't you kinda owe me?

10:05.147 --> 10:07.357
It was that lightweight idiot
working for me.

10:08.275 --> 10:10.027
He's into synthetic psychedelics.

10:10.110 --> 10:11.945
Like that real Burning Man shit.

10:12.029 --> 10:13.030
Hallucinogens?

10:13.113 --> 10:14.948
Yeah. Why?

10:15.908 --> 10:17.701
I saw this doctor.

10:19.161 --> 10:21.914
He said they can help you remember.

10:23.207 --> 10:26.418
Create new cerebral connections.

10:27.211 --> 10:28.253
What kind of doctor?

10:29.338 --> 10:31.256
It was just on the Internet.

10:32.382 --> 10:34.468
You don't want to try this shit, trust me.

10:36.345 --> 10:38.555
They make it in a garage in Richmond.

10:38.639 --> 10:41.141
Not exactly what I'd call quality control.

10:55.030 --> 10:56.031
Sorry.

10:56.823 --> 10:58.408
Comes with the territory.

10:59.868 --> 11:01.328
You don't have to apologize.

11:18.887 --> 11:22.891
Pretty soon this will all be over.
All you have to do is be yourself.

11:51.587 --> 11:54.006
Sophie, it's Hannah.

11:54.965 --> 11:56.633
I missed you today.

11:58.177 --> 12:01.180
<i>I know what I told you last time
shook you up.</i>

12:03.056 --> 12:08.562
<i>James and I, we only hid this from you
because we were trying to protect you.</i>

12:10.772 --> 12:12.566
<i>I'm worried about you, Sophie.</i>

12:14.735 --> 12:17.487
Please call me back.

12:26.747 --> 12:27.956
Is it good stuff?

12:31.335 --> 12:35.088
Speaking of stuff,
did you happen to bring the pills?

12:35.172 --> 12:38.008
I mean, if you didn't, it's okay.
I can wait or whatever.

12:38.091 --> 12:39.968
- Is this it?
- What do you mean?

12:40.052 --> 12:42.679
- There's nothing here.
- No, I downloaded everything there was.

12:42.763 --> 12:45.933
I asked for actual proof.
Account numbers, transaction histories.

12:46.683 --> 12:49.019
All you delivered was some petty expenses
and his Pornhub history,

12:49.102 --> 12:51.396
which is probably yours, considering
you've been jacking off all day.

12:51.480 --> 12:53.232
Look, I'm trying to be cool here, man.

12:53.899 --> 12:56.109
Okay, but that's everything, I swear.

12:56.777 --> 12:58.737
I risked my fucking life
to get those files.

12:58.820 --> 12:59.905
Jesus Christ.

13:04.993 --> 13:08.080
Look, he's got a laptop
that he takes home every night.

13:08.163 --> 13:11.375
If there was something illegal,
it'd be smart to put it on there, right?

13:11.458 --> 13:13.502
That way admin doesn't have the password.

14:01.175 --> 14:02.176
What?

14:03.719 --> 14:06.180
